---
---

<div class="coach-card">
  <div class="coach-header">
    <svg class="sparkle-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M10 0L12.2 7.8L20 10L12.2 12.2L10 20L7.8 12.2L0 10L7.8 7.8L10 0Z" fill="currentColor"/>
    </svg>
    <span class="coach-title">Runlab Coach</span>
  </div>

  <div class="chat-messages">
    <div class="message coach-message">
      <p>Your recovery score is high (84%) but your TSB is -12 after yesterday's long run. Should we scale back today's tempo?</p>
    </div>

    <div class="message user-message">
      <p>Yes, let's swap for a 30min recovery run. How does that impact Sunday's mileage?</p>
    </div>

    <div class="message coach-message">
      <p>Swapping to recovery today preserves your CTL at 47. We'll still hit our weekly target of 42mi. Sunday remains a 12mi aerobic base run.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="chat-input">
    <span class="input-placeholder">Ask about your training...</span>
    <svg class="send-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M3 10L17 10M17 10L11 4M17 10L11 16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .coach-card {
    background: var(--color-surface, #1A1A1A);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-surface-border, rgba(51, 97, 193, 0.15));
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    max-width: 460px;
    width: 100%;
    font-family: var(--font-body, 'Manrope', sans-serif);
  }

  .coach-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .sparkle-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-brand-blue);
  }

  .coach-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text, #FFFFFF);
  }

  .chat-messages {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .message p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .coach-message {
    background: var(--color-surface-high);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #888888);
    max-width: 90%;
  }

  .user-message {
    background: var(--color-brand-blue, #3361C1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    color: var(--color-text, #FFFFFF);
    max-width: 80%;
    align-self: flex-end;
  }

  .chat-input {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: var(--color-surface-high);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
  }

  .input-placeholder {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }

  .send-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-brand-blue);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .coach-card {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
